snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Real Madrid 3-1 Man City | Mbappe (3) & Nico Goals
snippet.description:
Manchester City were knocked out this seasonâ€™s UEFA Champions League after a 6-3 aggregate defeat to Real Madrid.
Pep Guardiolaâ€™s side were beaten 3-1 in the second leg at the Santiago Bernabeu with Kylian Mbappe scoring a hat-trick for the current European champions.

After a 3-2 defeat in the first leg at the Etihad, City fell further behind in the tie when the Frenchman scored the opener after just four minutes.

And we suffered a further early early setback with John Stones going off injured after just eight minutes while Erling Haaland was unable to feature in the fixture.

Mbappe scored two more either side of half-time before Nico scored his first goal for City in the dying minutes.

snippet.title: KABULI PULAO | Afghani Biryani Style Rice | Afghanistan Special Recipe Cooking In Indian Village
snippet.description:
In this video, we bring the delicious and traditional Kabuli Pulao, a special rice dish from Afghanistan, cooked in our Indian village style. This flavorful pulao is made with fragrant basmati rice, tender meat, sweet carrots, and raisins, giving it a perfect balance of sweetness and spices.

Watch as we prepare this Afghani biryani-style rice using natural village cooking methods over a firewood stove. This is a must-try recipe for all pulao and biryani lovers!

We follow our traditional village cooking style using fresh ingredients and firewood. The result is an authentic, mouthwatering dish that you can easily try at home!

The beneficiaries of the free electricity scheme in Rajasthan will get 150 units of free electricity.. but under the PM Surya Ghar Free Electricity Scheme.. that is, if you want to get free electricity now, then you will have to first install a solar plant at home under the PM Surya Ghar Scheme.. The Finance Minister made it clear in his speech that the government's objective behind this is to control the financial burden.. In such a situation, the question now is whether there is a big discrepancy in the government's announcement of free electricity.. Will the common consumers not get the benefit of free electricity now..? Will only the consumers who install solar plants get the benefit of this scheme.. Will the government bear the cost of installing solar plants..? And the question is also that will the consumers who are getting the benefit of 100 units of free electricity till now continue to get this relief even if they do not install a solar plant..?

snippet.description:

âœ”ï¸ Unprotected sexual contact
âœ”ï¸ Sharing needles or syringes
âœ”ï¸ From mother to child (during pregnancy, childbirth, or breastfeeding)
âœ”ï¸ Blood transfusions (though rare due to screening)

Stay informed and take precautions to prevent HIV transmission. If you found this video helpful, donâ€™t forget to like, share, and subscribe for more health awareness content!

"Na Kajre Ki Dhaar", is from the classic Bollywood movie Mohra (1994). It is one of the most iconic and memorable songs from the 90s. The song is beautifully composed by Viju Shah and sung by Sadhana Sargam and Pankaj Udhas. The lyrics were written by Indeevar. It features Poonam Jhaver and Suniel Shetty in a romantic dance sequence that became quite popular due to its catchy rhythm and the intense chemistry between the lead actors.

snippet.title: VIKRANT GUPTA REPORT ON PAKISTAN DEFEAT: Did Babarâ€™s Slow Batting Led to Pak loss? Pak vs NZ
snippet.description:
Babar Azam and Khushdil Shah scored gritty half centuries but Pakistan lost by 60 runs to New Zealand, their 4th straight defeat to the Kiwis, in the first match of the Champions Trophy 2025 at the National Stadium in Karachi on Wednesday. The Men in Green lost wickets at regular intervals and opener Fakhar Zamanâ€™s injury did not help matters as the Kiwis raced away with the win thanks to William ORourke and Mitchell Santner taking 3 wickets apiece.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

snippet.description:
In this video I take my subscribers on an all sponsored trip to Indiaâ€™s coldest place - Drass! The idea to share real & raw experiences with all of you, to make you experience what I experienced when I first reached this winter wonderland and to survive this we need some quality gear from Decathlon! 
Linking all of them below (Must Have for Snow & Cold) 


1. Gloves : https://www.decathlon.in/qr/8655827/-1

2  Trekking Shoe : https://www.decathlon.in/p/8319097/men-shoes/men-waterproof-trekking-shoes-mid-ankle-with-cross-contact-grip-grey-mt100

3. Neck Warmer :  https://www.decathlon.in/qr/8042436/-1 

4. Snow Pants :  https://www.decathlon.in/qr/8881425/-1

5. Down Jacket:  https://www.decathlon.in/qr/8495234/-1



How to reach Drass in peak winters? 
Situated in Kargil district of Ladakh this wonderland is easily accessable from Srinagar via Sonamarg and Zojila Pass but due to heavy snow route shuts down in winters and the only possible route that is left is you fly to Leh then take a cab Kargil and then fuethur to Drass!

Nayab is a simple girl who, after losing her parents, lives with her grandmother and brother. Her sister-in-law takes advantage of her simplicity, burdening her with all household chores and stunting her personal growth.

Zaviyaar, a successful man from a wealthy family, is paired with Nayab by his grandmother due
to her naivety and simplicity. After rebelling against his family and rejecting his cousin Tania to marry Nayab, Zaviyaar soon becomes frustrated with her lack of education and grooming. Hurt by Zaviyaarâ€™s rejection, Tania increases the rift between Nayab and Zaviyaar, causing tension and conflict in their marriage.

Will Zaviyaar and Nayabâ€™s marriage withstand the schemes of Tania? Can Nayab change herself for Zaviyaar? Will she find support from Zaviyaarâ€™s family, or will she face everything alone? Will Zaviyaar regret marrying Nayab? Will Tania be able to separate Zaviyaar and Nayab?
